PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773501073
OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMore than one in three (36%) school
OL,8,Fand college leaders say their students
OL,9,For teachers have experienced racial
OL,10,Fharassment while on the school
OL,11,Fcommute, a survey of ASCL members
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FIt comes after the government
OL,15,Fannounced a strategy on social
OL,16,Fcohesion to promote integration,
OL,17,Ftackle religious hatred and clamp down
OL,18,Fon extremist influence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773501073
OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FIn his speech at ASCL's annual
OL,8,Fconference, Mr Di'Iasio is expected to
OL,9,Fsay: "I worry when I see some
OL,10,Fpoliticians speaking about immigration
OL,11,Fas a problem that needs to be solved,
OL,12,Findulging in some sort of arms race
OL,13,Fabout how tough they are going to be
OL,14,Fon those who come to our country
OL,15,Fseeking asylum.
OL,17,F"I worry when I see flags tied to
OL,18,Flampposts, as we did last summer,
OL,19,Fsomething which seems more like a
OL,20,Fbrand of provocative nationalism than
OL,21,Fof proud patriotism."
OL,26,@qD@FOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773501073
OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FAdding: "I would encourage everyone to
OL,8,Ftake care with the language they use.
OL,9,FWords and actions have consequences in
OL,10,Fthe real world."
OL,12,FAn ASCL survey of 567 school and
OL,13,Fcollege leaders found more than one in
OL,14,Fthree (38%) said their students and
OL,15,Fstaff were worried about them or their
OL,16,Ffamilies being at risk from racial
OL,17,Fharassment or attack over the past
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773501073
OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FOne in 10 (11%) said the harassment
OL,8,Fstudents or staff have experienced on
OL,9,Fthe way to or from school has involved
OL,10,Fphysical attacks.
OL,12,FAsked whether she agreed with concerns
OL,13,Fabout divisions, Education Secretary
OL,14,FBridget Phillipson told reporters: "I
OL,15,Fbelieve we're a tolerant, diverse
OL,16,Fnation, where we have shared values
OL,17,Fand where we celebrate our national
OL,18,Fidentity.
OL,26,@vD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773501073
OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"That should be inclusive, we should
OL,8,Fall be able to celebrate our national
OL,9,Fidentity, the flags that represent the
OL,10,Fnations of our union, and that's
OL,11,Fimportant.
OL,13,F"And schools of course have an
OL,14,Fimportant role to play in making sure
OL,15,Fthat young people are well-equipped
OL,16,Ffor the world to come and emerge from
OL,17,Fschool as involved citizens."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
