OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FHeadteachers responding to the survey
OL,8,Fcited tensions fuelled by social
OL,9,Fmedia, anti-immigration rhetoric and
OL,10,Fcampaigns to display St George flags
OL,11,Fas causing them concern.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FSocial media platforms must take more
OL,19,Fresponsibility for policing sites and
OL,20,Fremoving toxic content, Mr Di'Iasio is
OL,21,Fexpected to say.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
