PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773501073
OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"If they are not going to do that
OL,8,Fvoluntarily, they should be made to do
OL,9,Fso through regulation," he will add.
OL,11,FMost heads (90%) said stronger social
OL,12,Fmedia platform regulation could help
OL,13,Faddress racist attitudes and
OL,14,Fbehaviour, and more care taken in the
OL,15,Flanguage politicians use about
OL,16,Fimmigration (83%).
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@WO]
