OL,3,CFamilies living in fear of racial
OL,4,Charassment, headteachers' union boss
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FThe government has launched a
OL,8,Fconsultation on keeping children safe
OL,9,Fonline, inviting views on whether
OL,10,Fthere should be an Australia-style ban
OL,11,Fon children from using social media,
OL,12,Fand at what age this could begin.
OL,14,FHowever, MPs voted earlier in the week
OL,15,Fto reject an amendment to the
OL,16,FChildren's Wellbeing and Schools Bill
OL,17,Fbacked by peers to ban social media
OL,18,Ffor under-16s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
